  Copyright
  ---------

The CineTracer-copyright is the same as the WaveTracer®-copyright, because
CineTracer is a part of the whole WaveTracer-DS®-softwarepackage. If a program
or a part of a program says something others, the maincopyright isn't valid.
  To get informations about the complete copyright, please have a look into
